= SDL_GetWindowGrab =
Use this function to get a window's input grab mode.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_GetWindowGrab(SDL_Window* window)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the window to query
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 1 if input is grabbed and 0 otherwise.

